PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781866972
OL,3,CChurch of England apologises for
OL,4,C'shameful' role in forced adoption
OL,6,FIn the years that followed, she
OL,7,Fstruggled mentally from what she went
OL,8,Fthrough in the home and was diagnosed
OL,9,Fwith post traumatic stress disorder.
OL,11,FWhen she tried to find her daughter
OL,12,Fshe was told all the records had been
OL,13,Fburnt in a fire.
OL,15,FMrs Davies went on to marry her
OL,16,Fdaughter's father Tony Davies, who had
OL,17,Fboth been 15 when their first child
OL,18,Fwas born.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/22
