OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781866972
OL,3,CChurch of England apologises for
OL,4,C'shameful' role in forced adoption
OL,6,FMr Davies described the guilt he felt
OL,7,Fas his then-girlfriend was sent away
OL,8,Fto have their baby in secret.
OL,10,F"I never even had the chance to see my
OL,11,Fdaughter," he told ITV News. "We were
OL,12,Ftreated disgracefully because we were
OL,13,Fyoung."
OL,15,FThirty years later, the couple were
OL,16,Ffinally reunited with their daughter
OL,17,FClaire - who they had named Mary at
OL,18,Fbirth - after she tracked them down
OL,19,Fusing a private detective.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
