OL,3,CChurch of England apologises for
OL,4,C'shameful' role in forced adoption
OL,6,F"I was cheated out of the childhood I
OL,7,Fshould have had with them," she told
OL,8,FITV News.
OL,10,FThe family have now built up a close
OL,11,Fbond, but they want accountability for
OL,12,Fthe life-long trauma they have endured.
OL,14,F'I wasn't adopted or fostered because
OL,15,FI was not white'
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/22
