OL,3,CChurch of England apologises for
OL,4,C'shameful' role in forced adoption
OL,6,FITV News has also heard shocking
OL,7,Ftestimony from Black and mixed
OL,8,Fheritage adoptees and care-leavers who
OL,9,Ffaced "abhorrent" racism and prejudice
OL,10,Fduring their time in Church of England-
OL,11,Frun homes.
OL,13,FFrom the moment Phil Frampton was born
OL,14,Fin 1953, his care records show that he
OL,15,Fwas treated with prejudice and
OL,16,Fdiscrimination because of the colour
OL,17,Fof his skin, with racist language used
OL,18,Fthroughout.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
