PN,31913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781866972
OL,3,CChurch of England apologises for
OL,4,C'shameful' role in forced adoption
OL,6,FHe told ITV News: "When I was a baby
OL,7,Fthe matron wrote: 'Philip is such a
OL,8,Fpoor specimen of humanity and there
OL,9,Fare doubts about his intelligence'."
OL,11,FHis mother, Mavis Frampton, had sought
OL,12,Frefuge at the Rosemundy Home for
OL,13,FUnmarried Mothers in St Agnes in
OL,14,FCornwall, which was linked to the
OL,15,FChurch of England, hundreds of miles
OL,16,Faway from her home in Birmingham.
OL,18,FInstead of help, she was told to pray
OL,19,Ffor forgiveness and labelled a fallen
OL,20,Fwoman.
OL,26,@nD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/22
