CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781866972
OL,3,CChurch of England apologises for
OL,4,C'shameful' role in forced adoption
OL,6,FHe grew up in orphanages in the south
OL,7,Fwest of England and then later
OL,8,Fchildren's homes in the north west. At
OL,9,Fone point he was even sent to a home
OL,10,Ffor disabled children, despite having
OL,11,Fno disabilities.
OL,13,FResponding to our investigation, the
OL,14,FArchbishop accepted the Church held
OL,15,Fresponsibility for the discrimination
OL,16,Fsuffered by those children.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
