PN,31916
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781866972
OL,3,CChurch of England apologises for
OL,4,C'shameful' role in forced adoption
OL,6,FIt concludes there were "dehumanising
OL,7,Fand dismissive attitudes, falling
OL,8,Fshort of what would be expected
OL,9,Ftowards anyone in the church's care".
OL,11,FAnnual records from the homes
OL,12,Ffrequently showed there were funding
OL,13,Fpressures, staffing problems and
OL,14,Fsubstandard conditions.
OL,16,FArchives from the Church's Board for
OL,17,FSocial Responsibility (BSR) which set
OL,18,Fthe tone and guidance of the homes
OL,19,Fover three decades, provide a chilling
OL,20,Finsight into their attitudes at the
OL,21,Ftime.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31917
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781866972
OL,3,CChurch of England apologises for
OL,4,C'shameful' role in forced adoption
OL,6,FDocuments from 1970 show how the homes
OL,7,Fare described as places "from which
OL,8,Fthe adoption agencies get their raw
OL,9,Fmaterials, while some mothers were
OL,10,Fdescribed as 'dim, feckless, (and)
OL,11,Finadequate'".
OL,13,F"Many will draw comfort in knowing
OL,14,Fthat their suffering has at long last
OL,15,Fbeen acknowledged," a spokesperson for
OL,16,Fthe campaign group Movement for an
OL,17,FAdoption Apology (MAA) said.
OL,26,@rD@^pmrD@bpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31918
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781866972
OL,3,CChurch of England apologises for
OL,4,C'shameful' role in forced adoption
OL,6,F"For the Church, this is their first
OL,7,Fstep on a long road to redemption. For
OL,8,Fthose affected, this is a moment to
OL,9,Freflect on these words, then ask the
OL,10,FChurch to provide real and tangible
OL,11,Fsupport.
OL,13,F"For this apology to carry weight and
OL,14,Fbe meaningful, it must be bolstered by
OL,15,Fmeasures which will help all survivors
OL,16,Fof the atrocities committed."
OL,18,FLambeth palace has said these words of
OL,19,Fapology are just the start, and that
OL,20,Fthe Church intends to provide more
OL,21,Fsupport for survivors.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
