PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781866972
OL,3,CChurch of England apologises for
OL,4,C'shameful' role in forced adoption
OL,6,FSome will be able to apply for a
OL,7,Fredress scheme, set up through an
OL,8,Findependent body, Archbishop Mullally
OL,9,Fconfirmed to ITV News.
OL,11,F"There will be an opportunity for
OL,12,Fpeople, if they feel they want, to
OL,13,Fsubmit an application to that," she
OL,14,Fsaid. "And that's not just about
OL,15,Ffinance, it's about redress that
OL,16,Frelates to spiritual, emotional,
OL,17,Ftherapeutic care as well."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31920
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781866972
OL,3,CChurch of England apologises for
OL,4,C'shameful' role in forced adoption
OL,6,FThe Church has also said that over the
OL,7,Fsummer, dioceses across England will
OL,8,Fbe holding special services to
OL,9,Fremember those who suffered.
OL,11,FThe commemorations will pay tribute to
OL,12,Fthose affected and the many who have
OL,13,Fdied waiting for justice.
OL,15,FThursday's announcement by the Church
OL,16,Fof England will increase the pressure
OL,17,Fon the government to make a formal
OL,18,Fapology for the state's role in
OL,19,Fhistorical forced adoption.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
