CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781866972
OL,3,CChurch of England apologises for
OL,4,C'shameful' role in forced adoption
OL,6,FThe government said it will make a
OL,7,F"full apology" for forced adoption in
OL,8,FEngland, Education Secretary Bridget
OL,9,FPhillipson has said.
OL,11,FPhillipson told the Education
OL,12,FCommittee on Wednesday that the
OL,13,Fhistorical practice was a "shameful
OL,14,Fperiod" in the country's history.
OL,16,FIn March, Sir Keir Starmer told ITV
OL,17,FNews his "instinct" is to issue a
OL,18,Fgovernment apology for the state's
OL,19,Frole in the forced adoption scandal.
OL,20,FThis now looks like it could happen in
OL,21,Fweeks.
